south
surname Nan

sentences.english: Modernized base of Chinese herbal medicine in south Shaanxi has entered all-round construction period.
sentences.chinese: 陕南现代化中草药基地进入全面建设阶段。

sentences.english: CHULIU has been popular in land business of south Shaanxi Province.
sentences.chinese: “除留”是广泛存在于陕南土地交易中的一种习惯。

sentences.english: Ming and Qing Dynasties were important period for the commoditization of agriculture in the south of Shaanxi Province.
sentences.chinese: 明清时期是陕南农业商品化发展的重要时期。

sentences.english: Cold noodles are a local dish in Southern Shaanxi and Central Shaanxi.
sentences.chinese: 凉皮是陕西关中及陕南地区的传统小吃。

sentences.english: Landslide and mudflow are main physic geological phenomena in the mountainous region of Southern Shaanxi.
sentences.chinese: 滑坡和泥石流是陕南山地成灾的主要物理地质现象。

sentences.english: The Donggouba area lies on the north rim of "Mian-Lue-Yang trigonalgeological zone" in southern Shanxi.
sentences.chinese: 东沟坝地区位于陕南“勉略阳三角地带”北缘。
